@page "/solutions/restaurants"
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components

<PageTitle>Restaurants — DMD StockShopOnline</PageTitle>

<div class="sol-hero">
    <div class="sol-hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-left">
            <div class="sol-eyebrow">
                <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
                Built for restaurants
            </div>
            <h1 class="sol-title">Run the kitchen.<br /><span class="sol-accent">Not the spreadsheet.</span></h1>
            <p class="sol-sub">Between ingredient costs rising, staff turnover, and tables to turn — the last thing you need is an inventory system that adds to the chaos. DMD keeps your stock, purchases, and finances under control so you can focus on the food.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/contact?plan=restaurant" class="btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
                <a href="/pricing" class="btn-ghost">See pricing</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-right">
            <div class="proof-card">
                <div class="proof-header">
                    <div class="proof-avatar purple-avatar">LT</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="proof-name">Leila T.</div>
                        <div class="proof-role">Owner, Lebanese restaurant · Toronto</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="proof-quote">"We use DMD for our retail side — packaged sauces and dry goods we sell to go. The purchase order system and expense tracking alone saved us hours every week."</p>
                <div class="proof-stat-row">
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">2h</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">saved per week</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">100%</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">expense visibility</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">14d</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">free to try</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="sol-page">

    <div class="pains-section">
        <div class="pains-label">Sound familiar?</div>
        <div class="pains-grid">
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Food costs are creeping up but you don't know exactly which items are killing your margin</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>You're manually tracking supplier invoices across email, paper, and memory</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Your retail side (packaged items, drinks, sauces) has no proper inventory system</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Cash sessions aren't being reconciled and you suspect discrepancies at end of day</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="note-banner">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        <p><strong>A note on fit:</strong> DMD is purpose-built for retail inventory and POS — not a full table management or kitchen display system. It's the right fit for restaurants that also sell packaged goods, run a counter service, or need tight control over their purchasing and retail operations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="solutions-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Where DMD adds value for restaurants</h2>
        <div class="sol-cards">

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon purple-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Control your purchasing costs</h3>
                <p>Create purchase orders for every supplier delivery. Track what you paid last time and compare it to the new invoice — catching a price increase before you accept it is worth more than any discount.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Purchase orders</span>
                    <span class="tag">Last purchase cost</span>
                    <span class="tag">Supplier directory</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon teal-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Counter service &amp; retail POS</h3>
                <p>For restaurants with a counter, grab-and-go section, or retail shelf — DMD's POS handles it. Search by product, process cash or card, and all stock deducts automatically.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Counter POS</span>
                    <span class="tag">Cash &amp; card</span>
                    <span class="tag">Stripe Terminal</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon green-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Understand your true expenses</h3>
                <p>Log every expense — food costs, labour, rent, utilities — by category. The financial dashboard shows revenue vs expenses vs net income for any period. Know if a slow month was a loss before it's too late.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Expense tracking</span>
                    <span class="tag">Financial dashboard</span>
                    <span class="tag">Net income report</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon navy-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Retail inventory for packaged goods</h3>
                <p>Selling bottled sauces, spice mixes, or beverages to go? DMD tracks every unit across your storage and front-of-house. Stock movements log every sale and delivery automatically.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Packaged goods</span>
                    <span class="tag">Live stock levels</span>
                    <span class="tag">Stock movements</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon orange-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Cash reconciliation you can trust</h3>
                <p>Each register has its own session. Open with a float, close with a count. The difference is calculated automatically — so you know exactly what your staff processed and what should be in the drawer.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Cash sessions</span>
                    <span class="tag">Per-register tracking</span>
                    <span class="tag">Session history</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon blue-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Staff access without the risk</h3>
                <p>Give servers and cashiers POS access only. Keep reports and financials locked to managers and owners. Every transaction is logged with who processed it, giving you full accountability.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Role-based access</span>
                    <span class="tag">Audit trail</span>
                    <span class="tag">Multi-user</span>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-more">
        <h2>Also built for</h2>
        <div class="explore-grid">
            <a href="/solutions/retail" class="explore-card">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <div class="explore-name">Retail Stores</div>
                    <div class="explore-desc">General &amp; specialty retail</div>
                </div>
                <svg class="explore-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/solutions/dry-goods" class="explore-card">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 2h18l-2 7H5L3 2z"/><path d="M5 9l-1 13h16L19 9"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <div class="explore-name">Nuts &amp; Dry Goods</div>
                    <div class="explore-desc">Bulk &amp; weight-based inventory</div>
                </div>
                <svg class="explore-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sol-cta">
        <h2>Ready to get your operations under control?</h2>
        <p>14-day free trial. No credit card. Set up in under an hour.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
            <a href="/contact?plan=restaurant" class="btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
            <a href="/features" class="btn-ghost">See all features</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<style>
    :root {
        --teal: #00BFA5;
        --teal-dark: #00897B;
        --teal-light: #E0F7F4;
        --navy: #1A237E;
        --navy-light: #E8EAF6;
        --text: #1C1C1E;
        --text-muted: #6B7280;
        --border: #E5E7EB;
        --surface: #F9FAFB;
        --white: #FFFFFF;
    }

    .sol-hero {
        background: #FFFFFF;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .sol-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        right: -100px;
        bottom: -100px;
        width: 400px;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,58,237,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .sol-hero-inner {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .sol-eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        background: #F3E5F5;
        border: 1px solid rgba(123,31,162,0.2);
        color: #4A148C;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.09em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 5px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        width: fit-content;
    }

    .eyebrow-dot {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #7B1FA2;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .sol-title {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.12;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .sol-accent { color: #4A148C; }
    .sol-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1.75rem; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .btn-primary {
        display: inline-block;
        background: var(--teal);
        color: #FFFFFF;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); }

    .btn-ghost {
        display: inline-block;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--teal); color: var(--teal-dark); }

    .proof-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .proof-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .proof-avatar {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #F3E5F5;
        color: #4A148C;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .proof-name { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .proof-role { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 1px; }

    .proof-quote {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-style: italic;
        border-left: 3px solid #7B1FA2;
        padding-left: 0.875rem;
        margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .proof-stat-row { display: flex; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; }

    .proof-stat {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2px;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .proof-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .proof-stat-num {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #4A148C;
    }

    .proof-stat-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; }

    .sol-page { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; }

    .pains-section { padding: 3rem 0 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    .pains-label {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #9CA3AF;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .pains-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .pain-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 10px;
        background: #FFF8F8;
        border: 1px solid #FEE2E2;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .pain-icon { color: #EF4444; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .pain-item p { font-size: 0.825rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }

    .note-banner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 10px;
        background: #EFF6FF;
        border: 1px solid #BFDBFE;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        color: #1E40AF;
    }

    .note-banner svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

    .note-banner p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        color: #1E3A8A;
    }

    .section-heading { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 1.75rem; }

    .sol-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .sol-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .sol-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--teal);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,191,165,0.08);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .sol-card-icon {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .teal-icon { background: var(--teal-light); color: var(--teal-dark); }
    .navy-icon { background: var(--navy-light); color: var(--navy); }
    .green-icon { background: #E8F5E9; color: #2E7D32; }
    .purple-icon { background: #F3E5F5; color: #7B1FA2; }
    .orange-icon { background: #FFF3E0; color: #E65100; }
    .blue-icon { background: #E3F2FD; color: #1565C0; }

    .sol-card h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
    .sol-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .sol-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }

    .tag {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 3px 8px;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .explore-more { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .explore-more h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 1rem; }

    .explore-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .explore-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--text);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .explore-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-light); }
    .explore-card svg:first-child { color: var(--teal-dark); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .explore-name { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .explore-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
    .explore-arrow { margin-left: auto; color: var(--text-muted); flex-shrink: 0; }

    .sol-cta { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .sol-cta h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 0.6rem; }
    .sol-cta p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 0 1.75rem; }
    .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    @@media (max-width: 700px) { .sol-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; } }
    @@media (max-width: 640px) { .sol-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .pains-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
